          <div class="additional-info" id="t1">
            <p> For his contributions to the industry, DSC has been awarded the<strong>&nbsp;International Emmy Directorate Award</strong>&nbsp;at their 39th&nbsp;International Emmy Awards night in New York and has also been&nbsp;<strong>Honored with the Doctorate of Business Administration by the University of East London.</strong></p>
