        <h3 id="political">Political</h3>
        <p>DSC maintains a keen interest in changing the core definition of politics to a public welfare division. As per him, the politicians should purely dedicate their time and energy towards the service of the people of India. He has already started his political journey by working for the people of Haryana, by filing his nomination papers as an independent candidate for Rajya Sabha.</p>
        <hr/>
        <h3  id="entrepreneurial">Entrepreneurial</h3>
        <p>DSC, being a self made man and a true visionary, consistently demonstrated his ability to identify new businesses and lead them to the path of success. He has almost become the synonym to the word Entrepreneurship in India; with his substantial contribution to the nation’s economy. With his pioneering vision, the nation saw the emergence and birth of an entire private satellite television industry in itself, creating jobs for millions across the nation and the world. Leading the 4th generation of the 90 year old Essel Group, DSC has launched India’s first amusement part – Essel World, India’s first MNC – Essel Propack, India’s first, India’s first DTH service – Dish TV and many such more pioneering ventures, uplifting the nation’s economic stance. </p>
        <p>Now he is looking at only ideas which are meaningful for society and bringing Brand India in top 10 brand from it’s current status at number 17. Though work on improving India’s GDP will be at the core of his thinking.</p>
        <hr/>
        <h3 id="social">Social</h3>
        <p>DSC has made his mark as an influential philanthropist in India. He has set up TALEEM (Transnational Alternate Learning for Emancipation and Empowerment through Multimedia) to provide access to quality education through distance and open learning. He is also the Chairman of the Ekal Vidyalaya Foundation of India — a movement to eradicate illiteracy from rural and tribal India. The Foundation provides free education to millions of tribal children across 52,000 villages through one-teacher schools. He is the moving force behind the Global Vipassana Foundation — a trust set up to help people raise their spiritual quotient. DSC is also the Founder Chairman of Global Foundation for Civilization Harmony (India) (GFCH), an Eastern initiative for conflict avoidance and a partner of the United Nations Alliance of Civilization (UNAOC). The founder patrons of GFCH include His Holiness Dalai Lama and former President of India Dr. A.P.J. Abdul Kalam, among others.</p>
        <hr/>
        <h3 id="economy">Economy</h3>
        <p>DSC is constantly working on documenting India’s economic development pre and post independence to generate awareness and a stark differentiation between good and bad phases, in order to carve a path for the future. His key efforts are also towards eradicating black economy, which he believed is the biggest and worst enemy of the nation.</p>
        <hr/>
        <h3 id="community">Community</h3>
        <p>DSC proudly represents the Vaishya community of Aggarwals. The origin of this community goes back to a place called as Agroha, where it is believed that Goddess Laxmi gave Maharaj Agrarsain the blessings. DSC aims to unite the 300 sub communities in Vaishya, and also works towards helping the ones in need by mobilizing funds from the rich to the ones who are deprived. </p>
        <hr/>
        <h3 id="media">Media</h3>
        <p>DSC is rightly known a Media Moghul, with his pioneering efforts in launching the country’s first private satellite television channel - Zee TV, followed by the first 24 hours news channel – Zee News. DSC has invested immense time, efforts and energy in being a bridge between change seekers and change agents.</p>
        <hr/>
        <h3 id="family">Family</h3>
        <p>DSC is a Family man and makes it a point to spend as much time as he can with his loved ones. Most above, he consistently works towards the betterment of his home town Hissar, and for the people residing across Haryana. </p>
        <hr/>
        <h3 id="philanthropy">Philanthropy</h3>
        <p>DSC and his entire family have always practiced towards donating 10% of their profit towards an integrated DSC Foundation, which in turn works towards the upliftment of the society. </p>
        <hr/>
        <h3 id="motivator">Motivator</h3>
        <p>DSC continues to motivate the youth of India, by sharing his experience, knowledge and wisdom through his popular show titled as DSC Show. With this show, DSC reaches over 250 Mn viewers across the nation, enriching their minds and hearts. DSC makes it a point to personally respond to 100s of emails which he gets on a daily basis. </p>
        <hr/>
        <h3 id="cultural">Cultural</h3>
        <p>DSC practices Vipassana as per the teaching of Buddha, which keeps him calm and focused. He has built world’s largest pagoda in the suburbs of Mumbai, which is a very rare monument, where people practice Vipassana. DSC also espouses the belief of Vasudhaiva Kutumbakam, which means the entire World is One Family. </p>
        <hr/>
        <p>All 10 traits of SC, make him unique individual in Modern times. The combination of all above will position him to represent India Globally as well as he should be seen as an Economically, socially & politically evolved leader for youth & old alike with compassion, having a desire to help its nation with the philosophy of “Vasudhiva Khtumbakam”</p>
